SUMMARY:Dinner\, Movie\, and Discussion of Screenagers
DESCRIPTION:Join us in person at Cesar Chavez Elementary’s Muti-Puprose Room (MPR) for an engaging event featuring Screenagers! This event is perfect for families and educators looking to explore how kids engage with screens and technology. Come connect\, learn\, and share your thoughts in a relaxed\, friendly atmosphere. Don’t miss out on this chance to dive into the digital lives of our young ones together! \nThere will be pizza\, popcorn\, drinks\, snacks\, and candy for sale. \nThis casual dinner and a movie evening includes:\n• 1-hour film screening\n• 30-minute guided discussion afterwards \nA suggested donation of $5-10/person is appreciated to offset expenses. \nDonations are optional and no one will be turned away!
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/dinner-movie-and-discussion-of-screenagers/
LOCATION:Cesar Chavez Elementary\, 1221 Anderson Road\, Davis\, CA\, 95816\, United States
CATEGORIES:Bring the Kids,Community,Screen
